Vamos, toma mi mano.

00:38:14.890 --> 00:38:15.850
No, gracias.

00:38:17.970 --> 00:38:18.729
No.

00:38:19.370 --> 00:38:20.689
Estoy preocupado por ti.

00:38:21.249 --> 00:38:21.970
Sr. Lu.

00:38:22.810 --> 00:38:24.370
Iré a buscarte ahora.

00:38:25.850 --> 00:38:26.490
Peilan.

00:38:27.290 --> 00:38:29.770
Peilan.

00:39:03.569 --> 00:39:04.450
Duele.

00:39:06.810 --> 00:39:07.890
No estoy muerto.

